                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890422-72-victim669 t17890422-72-viclabel336"></join>, I lost the things in the indictment, in an inclosure; I had seen the things about twelve on the Sunday before, on the 22d of March; I missed them on the Monday morning, coming to plough again; I had seen the prisoner once or twice before, he had worked near me.</p>
